{"tid":719691,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[redvelvet]今日同wendy踩單車比mk仔追打.....18+","createTime":"2018-06-27T15:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T10:38:29.000Z","uid":52073,"like":21,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cf993081af49e415ff1f2501c3f652d28f404842","tid":719691,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:15:21.000Z","msg":"話說今日同wendy踩單車  我仲一邊踩單車一邊唱twice果首likey<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知後面突然有三個播住blackpink-ddu du ddu du既00後mk出黎撞鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見唔對路就諗住即刻加速 但我部輔助轆單車完全唔夠班mk既課金單車鬥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住我仲比班mk夾我三文治逼我磨牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我條褲仲比佢地磨爛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住我即刻<br />\n叫佢地賠錢 問佢地係咪搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢地竟然話我唱twice得罪佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲突然一拳打落我個肚到 我比佢地打到訓左係到 痛到我喊左-.-<br />\n<br />\nwendy見狀即刻落車幫我打鳩班mk 佢都幾好打 1個就打到果3條mk仔敗走 班00後mk真係唔識死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我就同wendy繼續快樂的單車之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我愛wendy!!"},{"pid":"5f713bb77477a5383ef2dfdf158750727562af9c","tid":719691,"uid":52073,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/231615_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F231615_ea3dc39ca0b2